lead_paragraph: Andy North is a two-time U.S. Open champion and analyst for ESPN at the Masters. Here are his answers for the AP's Masters trivia quiz. Incorrect answers are capitalized.

headline.print_headline: Who Knows Masters Trivia? Not Spieth and McIlroy
